 Eddie Van Halen plans to enter rehab. In a March 8 statement, the guitarist
for the hard rock band Van Halen said he will seek treatment for unspecified
reasons. He says he presently feels incapable of giving fans his best
performance.
It's not known whether Eddie Van Halen will be in New York City for Van Halen's
March 12 induction into the Rock and Roll Hall Of Fame.
